Has anyone plan on making a expansion pack for the tundra exploration mod to include the Starship Munship? I’ve tried KerbalX stuff but they’re impractical as they use the fairing glitch and excessive parts clipping. Would be a cool edition to KSP specialally if it where modeled in the same asthetic and is compatible with the tundra super heavy.

Edited July 13, 2021 by Cloakedwand72
